		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The first screen looks great, but I'm not a big fan of the boss. It looks awesome as an isolated bit of pixel art, but as an actual in-game object, it's too busy and doesn't have enough contrast, I feel like it doesn't match the tone set by the rest of the graphics, which are more stylized and well defined.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
